---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="SMS Consent & Opt-In | RevAgentic"
  description="How RevAgentic collects consent to send SMS messages to gym and fitness operators."
>
  <nav class="border-b border-brand-border bg-white px-6 py-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <span class="font-display font-bold text-brand-navy">revagentic<span class="text-brand-purple">.ai</span></span>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl text-brand-navy mb-4">SMS Messaging Consent</h1>
    <p class="text-brand-muted font-body text-lg mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      This page describes how Agentic Revenue Lab LLC (operating as RevAgentic) collects consent to send SMS messages, and what recipients can expect.
    </p>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">How You Opt In</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
        When you submit our Revenue Systems Diagnostic form or any contact form on revagentic.ai, you may provide your mobile phone number. By providing your number and checking the SMS consent checkbox on the form, you agree to receive SMS messages from RevAgentic (Agentic Revenue Lab LLC) related to your diagnostic results, follow-up communications, and information about our services.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-brand-bg border border-brand-border rounded-xl p-6 mb-4">
        <p class="font-display font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Example opt-in language shown at point of collection:</p>
        <p class="text-brand-muted font-body text-sm italic leading-relaxed">
          "By providing your phone number and checking this box, you agree to receive SMS messages from RevAgentic (Agentic Revenue Lab LLC) about your diagnostic results and follow-up information. Message frequency varies. Msg &amp; data rates may apply. Reply STOP to opt out at any time. Reply HELP for help."
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-brand-muted font-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Consent is never required as a condition of purchase. You may opt out at any time.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">What Messages You Will Receive</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-muted font-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <span class="text-brand-purple mt-0.5 font-bold">→</span>
          Your Revenue Systems Diagnostic results and report
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-muted font-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <span class="text-brand-purple mt-0.5 font-bold">→</span>
          Follow-up communications related to your inquiry
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-muted font-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <span class="text-brand-purple mt-0.5 font-bold">→</span>
          Information about RevAgentic services relevant to your business
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-muted font-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <span class="text-brand-purple mt-0.5 font-bold">→</span>
          Appointment reminders and scheduling confirmations
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Message Frequency and Rates</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">
        Message frequency varies based on your inquiry and engagement. Standard message and data rates may apply depending on your carrier and plan.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">How to Opt Out</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to any message to unsubscribe. You will receive a confirmation and no further messages will be sent. Reply <strong>START</strong> to resubscribe.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Help</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">
        Reply <strong>HELP</strong> to any message, or email <a href="mailto:hello@revagentic.ai" class="text-brand-purple hover:underline">hello@revagentic.ai</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Our SMS Number</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">
        SMS messages from RevAgentic are sent from <strong>+1 (855) 905-5409</strong>, a toll-free number operated by Agentic Revenue Lab LLC.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">
        Your phone number will never be sold or shared with third parties for marketing. See our <a href="/privacy" class="text-brand-purple hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="/terms" class="text-brand-purple hover:underline">Terms of Service</a> for full details.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-8">
      <p class="text-brand-muted font-body text-sm">
        Operated by <strong>Agentic Revenue Lab LLC</strong> d/b/a RevAgentic · hello@revagentic.ai · Chicago, IL
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-brand-border px-6 py-8 bg-white mt-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-brand-muted text-sm">
      <p>© 2026 RevAgentic. All rights reserved. RevAgentic is a service of Agentic Revenue Lab LLC.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
